import React, { Fragment } from 'react';
import { Button, Container, Header, Icon, Image } from 'semantic-ui-react';

import './Sidebar.css'
import headshot from '../images/headshot.png'

export default function Sidebar() {
  return (
    <Fragment>
      <Container>
        <Image
          src={headshot}
          circular
        >
        </Image>
        <Header as='h4' className='vert-center'>
          this is the sidebar
          this is another
          thing
          in
          the
          sidebar
        </Header>
      </Container>
    </Fragment>
  )
}
